  "id": "PLACE_cableway_berthroom",
  "label": "Cableway Berthroom",
  "description": "A compact berthroom cut into the ship’s braced ribs off the Cinderwake Cableway, its bulkheads faced in soot-dark plating and tarred rivet lines. A built-in bunk and narrow locker occupy opposite walls, their iron fittings wrapped in ash-seal cloth to blunt grit and vibration. The sole remains scoured and slightly crowned for drainage, with tether rings set low for securing gear in Vespera Tertius’ electrostatic gales. Light enters through a shuttered lantern slit, reduced to a controlled bar that keeps the space dim and heat-conserving.",
